            <div type="edition" subtype="transcription">
                <p><g>+</g> Ἐπὶ τῶν <expan><abbr>θεοφιλ</abbr><ex>εστάτων</ex></expan> Ἠλίου κὲ Νόννου κὲ Σελαμῶνος διακόνου
                    <lb/>ἐγένετο τὸ ἔργον τοῦτο <expan><abbr>κ</abbr><ex>αὶ</ex></expan> ἡ οἰκοδομὴ πᾶσα τοῦ μοναστηρίου <lb/>ἐν μηνὶ
                    Δισίου <expan><abbr>ἰνδ</abbr><ex>ικτιῶνος</ex></expan> ὀγδόης ἔτους τῆς <expan><abbr>πόλ</abbr><ex>εως</ex></expan> <num value="375">τοϛʹ</num>· κὲ Βαράχου. <g ref="palm"/></p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <p>Under the most God-loving Elias and Nonnos and Selamon deacon this work was done,
                    as well as the entire building of the monastery, in the month of Daesius of the
                    eighth indiction, year 376 of the city; also (under) Barachos.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p>The inscription gives the date of the construction of the monastery (the month of
                    Daisios in the eighth indiction, in the year 376 of the calendar of
                    Eluetheropolis (Beit Guvrin)). It also names the abbots Nunun and Elias.</p>
            </div>
        <div type="edition" subtype="transcription_segmented"><p><w xml:id="khur0002-1" xml:lang="grc">Ἐπὶ</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-2" xml:lang="grc">τῶν</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-3" xml:lang="grc"><expan><abbr>θεοφιλ</abbr><ex>εστάτων</ex></expan></w> <w xml:id="khur0002-4" xml:lang="grc">Ἠλίου</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-5" xml:lang="grc">κὲ</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-6" xml:lang="grc">Νόννου</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-7" xml:lang="grc">κὲ</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-8" xml:lang="grc">Σελαμῶνος</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-9" xml:lang="grc">διακόνου</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-10" xml:lang="grc">ἐγένετο</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-11" xml:lang="grc">τὸ</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-12" xml:lang="grc">ἔργον</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-13" xml:lang="grc">τοῦτο</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-14" xml:lang="grc"><expan><abbr>κ</abbr><ex>αὶ</ex></expan></w> <w xml:id="khur0002-15" xml:lang="grc">ἡ</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-16" xml:lang="grc">οἰκοδομὴ</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-17" xml:lang="grc">πᾶσα</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-18" xml:lang="grc">τοῦ</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-19" xml:lang="grc">μοναστηρίου</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-20" xml:lang="grc">ἐν</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-21" xml:lang="grc">μηνὶ</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-22" xml:lang="grc">Δισίου</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-23" xml:lang="grc"><expan><abbr>ἰνδ</abbr><ex>ικτιῶνος</ex></expan></w> <w xml:id="khur0002-24" xml:lang="grc">ὀγδόης</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-25" xml:lang="grc">ἔτους</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-26" xml:lang="grc">τῆς</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-27" xml:lang="grc"><expan><abbr>πόλ</abbr><ex>εως</ex></expan></w> <num xml:id="khur0002-28" value="375" xml:lang="grc">τοϛʹ</num> <w xml:id="khur0002-29" xml:lang="grc">κὲ</w> <w xml:id="khur0002-30" xml:lang="grc">Βαράχου.</w> </p>
